{"tid":2078893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方處理街頭集結案時遇襲22名警員傷","createTime":"2020-06-25T11:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:44:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60e9b72ef2413480cb4a3a706258d4ab3851336f","tid":2078893,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"英國倫敦警方處理一宗非法街頭集結案件時遇襲，22名警員受傷，亦有警車被破壞。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今日凌晨，警方到布里克斯頓區一個無牌音樂聚會，處理噪音及暴力投訴時，未能勸籲民眾離開，反而遇襲，警方拘捕4人，其中兩名警員需要送院。<br />\n<br />\n內政大臣彭黛玲譴責事件，形容是完全卑鄙的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534107-20200625.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534107-20200625.htm&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qfa0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=b5816b12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534107-20200625.htm&h=b54665bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534107-20200625.htm</a>"},{"pid":"151d152381dd38356593f0efcf800c504223c6fc","tid":2078893,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:34:25.000Z","msg":"［行動po置頂］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2078606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2078606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba1eedb1cc09daffc79431a14141f4e17c090a44","tid":2078893,"uid":4575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"開心左一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834a1f408cfc8d0abc5ebada2b9f79d5da4d6601","tid":2078893,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba1eedb1cc09daffc79431a14141f4e17c090a44","tid":2078893,"uid":4575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"開心左一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets